<div class="accordion-wrapper">
  <div class="custom-accordion">

    <!-- BENEFITS -->
    <details>
      <summary>BENEFITS</summary>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>1. Builds Strong Immunity</strong><br>
        Rich in antioxidants and natural enzymes, it strengthens your body’s defenses and supports overall wellness.</p>

        <p><strong>2. Promotes Digestive Health</strong><br>
        Its prebiotic nature nourishes gut-friendly bacteria, helping improve digestion and nutrient absorption.</p>

        <p><strong>3. Natural Energy Booster</strong><br>
        A wholesome source of instant energy that keeps you active and refreshed without refined sugar or additives.</p>

        <p><strong>4. Enhances Skin Glow</strong><br>
        Known for its antibacterial and moisturizing properties, it keeps your skin radiant, hydrated, and youthful.</p>

        <p><strong>5. Supports Weight Balance</strong><br>
        When taken with warm water, it helps improve metabolism and aids in natural weight management.</p>

        <p><strong>6. 100% Raw, Unfiltered & NMR Tested</strong><br>
        Sourced directly from wild Gir flora, every drop is unprocessed and NMR tested for purity.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- INGREDIENTS -->
    <details>
      <summary>INGREDIENTS & NUTRITION</summary>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>100% Organic Honey</strong></p>
        <p>No Preservatives | No Added Flavours | No Added Sugar | No Added Colors</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- MAKING PROCESS -->
    <details>
      <summary>MAKING PROCESS</summary>
      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>1. From the Heart of Gir Forests</strong><br>
        Bees collect nectar from the wild blossoms of Gir’s rich flora.</p>

        <p><strong>2. Naturally Crafted by Bees</strong><br>
        Nectar is transformed into honey inside natural honeycombs.</p>

        <p><strong>3. Harvested with Care</strong><br>
        Honeycombs are collected without harming bees or hives.</p>

        <p><strong>4. Cold-Extracted & Unprocessed</strong><br>
        Extracted naturally without heat to preserve nutrients.</p>

        <p><strong>5. Bottled in Its Purest Form</strong><br>
        NMR tested and packed in eco-friendly jars.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- STORAGE -->
    <details>
      <summary>STORAGE</summary>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Store in a cool & dry place.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- SHIPPING -->
    <details>
      <summary>SHIPPING & RETURN POLICY</summary>
      <div class="content">
        <p>We want you to love every drop of your purchase.</p>

        <p>If your order arrives damaged, leaked, or incorrect, please email us at loveofgir@gmail.com within 48 hours with photos.</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Returns accepted within 7 days (sealed products only)</li>
          <li>Full refund/replacement for damaged items</li>
          <li>Opened products cannot be returned</li>
          <li>Refund processed in 7–10 working days</li>
          <li>COD refunds via bank transfer</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Your happiness means the world to us ❤️</p>
      </div>
    </details>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
.accordion-wrapper {
  max-width: var(--page-width);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 1.5rem;
}

.custom-accordion {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.custom-accordion details {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  padding: 14px 18px;
}

.custom-accordion details:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.custom-accordion summary {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  color: #2f3e2f;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.custom-accordion summary::after {
  content: "+";
  font-size: 18px;
}

.custom-accordion details[open] summary::after {
  content: "−";
}

.custom-accordion .content {
  margin-top: 12px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #444;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.custom-accordion p {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.custom-accordion ul {
  padding-left: 18px;
}

.custom-accordion li {
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.custom-accordion summary:hover {
  color: #1b5e20;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .custom-accordion summary {
    font-size: 12px;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product Accordion",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Product Accordion"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
